568
00:37:51,602 --> 00:37:55,640
I heard Tae-gyung was with Mi-nam
at the time.

569
00:37:56,240 --> 00:37:57,275
Then...

570
00:37:57,341 --> 00:37:59,277
I should go ask Mi-nam

571
00:37:59,443 --> 00:38:01,746
