All right, you two!

580
00:38:28,572 --> 00:38:31,008
Act close, talk naturally.

581
00:38:31,509 --> 00:38:33,344
Ready, action!

582
00:38:35,880 --> 00:38:36,881
Ko Mi-nam.

583
