where you can give me advice?

590
00:39:04,775 --> 00:39:06,444
What, do you think
even if you quit A.N.JELL,

591
00:39:06,510 --> 00:39:10,147
you'll be future Mrs. Pharmacist,
so you've got nothing to be scared of?

592
