Like us?

652
00:43:05,516 --> 00:43:06,517
Yeah.

653
00:43:08,319 --> 00:43:09,320
That sounds so amazing.

654
00:43:09,386 --> 00:43:10,421
Oh, my.

655
00:43:10,487 --> 00:43:13,157
Do you like them that much?

656
00:43:13,691 --> 00:43:15,426
To me, they're just

657
