I would be devastated.

683
00:45:53,183 --> 00:45:55,753
But for us, it's a blessing!

684
00:45:55,819 --> 00:45:58,322
The stories these kids come up with.

685
00:45:58,756 --> 00:45:59,790
Hey.

686
00:45:59,957 --> 00:46:01,892
