719
00:48:05,849 --> 00:48:06,984
Mi-nam.

720
00:48:07,885 --> 00:48:09,219
Have you seen Tae-gyung?

721
00:48:09,753 --> 00:48:12,256
Weren't you filming together?

722
00:48:12,623 --> 00:48:14,791
