746
00:49:21,425 --> 00:49:22,426
Nothing.

747
00:49:24,628 --> 00:49:25,595
Ko Mi-nam.

748
00:49:25,896 --> 00:49:26,863
Hey.

749
00:49:29,466 --> 00:49:31,168
Dong-jun, have a safe trip

